Company Profile
UPDATES (4)
ASK  QUESTION







“ClimateStore is a mission-driven retail brand that supports people interested in taking personal action to address climate change. We curate and sell products and consolidate information for consumers to make climate friendly living easy. At ClimateStore you can learn about climate change, shop for solutions and find ideas that help address the issue of our time.



Steven Bushnell
Founder and CEO, ClimateStore




Key Facts

Social media interest from strong  brands including Ben & Jerry's, Microsoft, Audubon, Earth Institute, NASA, Treehugger and more.
30,000 followers with proven ability to attract 1500/mo with minimal effort.
500+ customers and 400 curated products from 30 suppliers.
28% Q/Q top line growth achieved from pilot efforts.
Numerous opportunities for sourcing low-carbon products and for partnerships with mission aligned institutions.

Our Ambition
Our goal is to build a high impact retail brand that will support climate friendly living. We believe there is a growing movement of people who want to take personal action and it will accelerate as climate change unfolds. We also think retail is an untapped opportunity for sharing ideas and building community. In 5 years we seek to be the go-to brand for people seeking sustainable solutions with revenues from website sales, partnerships, catalogs, marketplaces and ultimately physical stores.
