September  2, 2016
At the ClimateStore they think the evidence for human caused climate change is overwhelming. They trust the scientific experts who have painstakingly assessed the evidence and shown an indisputable link between our use of fossil fuels, greenhouse gas emissions, and the risk of irreversible global warming.
