News


ClimateStore, Inc. leased 2,915 SF at Walpole Station Business Center
PRESS RELEASE – 9/30/13
ClimateStore, Inc. joins a varied and strong tenant roster at Walpole Station Business Center (WSBC) with 2,915 SF of office and storage space.
Michael K. Manzo, Partner of The Manzo Company, represented the Owner.  “ClimateStore, Inc. adds an exciting new “e-tailer” startup to our roster with a focus on environmentally sustainable and carbon reducing consumer products. The deal speaks to the flexibility and creativity offered by ownership of the WSBC in accommodating a wide variety of commercial space needs.”
Property owned and managed by The Manzo Company, Tambone Investment Group and Old Hill Partners.
For more information or to inquire about space availability at Walpole Station Business Center, please contact Mike Jr.:
Michael K. Manzo, Partner
The Manzo Company
200 Wheeler Road, Suite 210
Burlington, MA 01803
O/F: 617.807.0963 ext. 702
M: 617.763.2402
mkmanzo@manzocompany.com
 







